We are as divided now
as we were before the Civil War.

38
00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:27.272
♪

39
00:02:27.355 --> 00:02:31.693
And we're not really getting
at the root causes.

40
00:02:31.734 --> 00:02:34.195
(indistinct chatter)

41
00:02:34.279 --> 00:02:38.199
What we have today
is a kind of party loyalty

42
00:02:38.241 --> 00:02:41.661
