our loyalty to our country.

43
00:02:41.703 --> 00:02:42.912
You don't belong here!

44
00:02:42.996 --> 00:02:44.414
You don't
belong here!

45
00:02:44.497 --> 00:02:46.916
What we're seeing today
is a dehumanizing

46
00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:50.545
of everyone who opposes us.

47
00:02:50.628 --> 00:02:52.547
If you ask people why
they're a Republican

48
00:02:52.630 --> 00:02:53.923
or why they're a Democrat:

49
00:02:54.007 --> 00:02:55.884
"It's because I hate
the other party."

50
00:02:55.925 --> 00:02:57.385
It sounds like
they're making arrests.

51
00:02:57.427 --> 00:03:00.054
