754
00:35:26.457 --> 00:35:27.708
Just grab something.

755
00:35:27.792 --> 00:35:29.669
It's all gonna be
handed out today.

756
00:35:29.710 --> 00:35:31.671
Thanks for taking us
around. man.

757
00:35:31.754 --> 00:35:34.298
This is really--really
kind of you to do this.

758
00:35:34.340 --> 00:35:35.424
Sure. sure.

759
00:35:35.508 --> 00:35:36.759
Tell me what you're doing today.

760
00:35:36.843 --> 00:35:39.762
-We feed hungry people.
