761
00:35:39.846 --> 00:35:41.139
So when you deliver this
to somebody.

762
00:35:41.180 --> 00:35:43.474
is it their only meal
of the day

763
00:35:43.516 --> 00:35:44.851
or just a good start
to the day?

764
00:35:44.934 --> 00:35:46.686
-What is here usually...
-Sometimes. they tell me

765
00:35:46.769 --> 00:35:48.396
they haven't eaten
in five days.

766
00:35:48.479 --> 00:35:50.189
Oh my gosh.

767
00:35:50.273 --> 00:35:51.774
♪

768
00:35:51.858 --> 00:35:54.402
-Hi. How are you?
-Good morning.

769
00:35:54.485 --> 00:35:55.653
I'm tagging along
with Bear today.

770
00:35:55.695 --> 00:35:57.071
-I'm David.
-Henry.

771
00:35:57.155 --> 00:35:59.532
-Good to meet you. Henry.
-Cranberries today.

772
00:35:59.574 --> 00:36:00.867
-Thank you.
