so I choose to be out here

777
00:36:09.542 --> 00:36:11.043
and I choose to drink.

778
00:36:11.085 --> 00:36:12.795
It's not good. though.
it's not good.

779
00:36:12.879 --> 00:36:14.922
I want to stop. it's just
gonna take me some time.

780
00:36:15.006 --> 00:36:17.216
Yeah. Is there support to stop?

781
00:36:17.300 --> 00:36:18.509
-I mean. like...
