782
00:36:18.551 --> 00:36:20.052
My family comes. they stop by.

783
00:36:20.136 --> 00:36:23.347
Yeah. they get mad at me.
stuff like that.

784
00:36:23.389 --> 00:36:26.017
So you know you're breaking
the law. right?

785
00:36:26.058 --> 00:36:29.103
Alcohol is illegal
