00:55:12.517 --> 00:55:15.270
It's just hard to imagine.

1205
00:55:15.353 --> 00:55:17.605
I wish there was
something I could do

1206
00:55:17.689 --> 00:55:20.525
to help her.

1207
00:55:20.608 --> 00:55:24.195
♪

1208
00:55:24.279 --> 00:55:27.115
I do meet a lot
of people who say.

1209
00:55:27.198 --> 00:55:30.201
