1214
00:55:37.542 --> 00:55:40.879
because we're all
ordinary people in the end.

1215
00:55:40.962 --> 00:55:43.423
But I think each of us
have a certain kind of power.

1216
00:55:43.506 --> 00:55:44.966
And at whatever level we live.

1217
00:55:45.050 --> 00:55:47.218
I think we make a difference.

1218
00:55:47.260 --> 00:55:50.221
Every time you interact
with someone else

1219
00:55:50.263 --> 00:55:54.059
you can either express
decency. and empathy. and care.

1220
00:55:54.142 --> 00:55:57.771
or fear. and animosity.
and judgment.

1221
00:55:57.854 --> 00:55:59.564
The key thing is to feel like

1222
00:55:59.606 --> 00:56:02.650
we're part of the solution
for our own lives.

1223
00:56:02.734 --> 00:56:04.778
♪

1224
00:56:04.861 --> 00:56:06.071
I went on this journey

1225
00:56:06.154 --> 00:56:08.406
