I am part of the problem.

1227
00:56:13.328 --> 00:56:17.082
It exposed something in myself
that I didn't wanna see

1228
00:56:17.165 --> 00:56:20.668
that's deeply rooted
in all of us.

1229
00:56:20.752 --> 00:56:22.837
the belief that certain people

1230
00:56:22.921 --> 00:56:26.383
have more value than others.

1231
00:56:26.424 --> 00:56:28.009
It has been hard for me
to come to terms

1232
00:56:28.093 --> 00:56:31.346
with the darkness
that lies inside of me.

1233
00:56:31.429 --> 00:56:35.850
And that darkness judges
people before I meet them.

1234
00:56:35.934 --> 00:56:37.102
And that's a.

1235
00:56:37.185 --> 00:56:39.437
that's a hard thing to face.

1236
00:56:41.272 --> 00:56:44.442
It was horrendously difficult

1237
00:56:44.526 --> 00:56:46.903
and full of tears.

1238
00:56:46.945 --> 00:56:48.780
asking the question.
"What in the hell

1239
00:56:48.863 --> 00:56:50.365
are we doing right now?

1240
00:56:50.448 --> 00:56:53.660
Why are we here?"

1241
00:56:53.743 --> 00:56:55.495
We have no home to return to.

1242
00:56:55.578 --> 00:56:57.205
We have no job to return to.

1243
00:56:57.288 --> 00:57:01.501
I've never felt more
irresponsible in my life.

1244
00:57:01.584 --> 00:57:04.129
but the transformation
that we're going through

1245
00:57:04.170 --> 00:57:07.549
in our minds.
and in our hearts

1246
00:57:07.632 --> 00:57:11.428
is worth every penny of this.

1247
00:57:11.469 --> 00:57:13.972
We felt a responsibility

1248
00:57:14.055 --> 00:57:16.015
to take these stories
and to share them

1249
00:57:16.099 --> 00:57:17.892
with people like me.

1250
00:57:17.976 --> 00:57:20.145
who don't know
there's a problem.

1251
00:57:20.186 --> 00:57:23.314
and that feels impossible.

1252
00:57:23.356 --> 00:57:25.150
♪

1253
00:57:25.191 --> 00:57:26.985
When I look at this nationally.

1254
00:57:27.068 --> 00:57:29.404
it's hard to be optimistic.

1255
00:57:29.487 --> 00:57:32.157
But meeting people
across the country

1256
00:57:32.240 --> 00:57:35.994
who have a passion
to see our divisions heal.

1257
00:57:36.077 --> 00:57:37.662
that gives me hope.

1258
00:57:37.704 --> 00:57:42.167
♪

1259
00:57:42.208 --> 00:57:44.043
There's no question
there are obstacles

1260
00:57:44.127 --> 00:57:45.670
