1284
00:58:43.895 --> 00:58:45.813
It feels like you're drowning.

1285
00:58:45.897 --> 00:58:47.232
and that's one of the reasons

1286
00:58:47.273 --> 00:58:49.150
I continue to work so hard

1287
00:58:49.234 --> 00:58:52.070
to break the stranglehold

1288
00:58:52.111 --> 00:58:56.282
because it's put us
in a very. very bad spot.

1289
00:58:56.366 --> 00:58:57.951
We're going to continue
to make progress.

1290
00:58:58.034 --> 00:59:01.204
but it's going
to take a long time.

