1501
01:08:36.654 --> 01:08:38.447
on our politics.

1502
01:08:38.489 --> 01:08:40.699
What has been the most
gratifying thing

1503
01:08:40.783 --> 01:08:44.078
is all of you
in this room tonight.

1504
01:08:44.161 --> 01:08:46.038
I've heard people say
that my family

1505
01:08:46.122 --> 01:08:48.916
is a little
overbearing at times.

1506
01:08:48.999 --> 01:08:52.044
